to,
the
statement
that
the Avalon
lithium hydroxide product would be a suitable precursor for the
synthesis of lithium and manganese-rich NMC-type cathode
materials
, that
Avalon has also identified opportunities to further improve the
purity of its initial lithium hydroxide product and will be
following up with further testwork in the near future
, tha
t t
his work will be supported by funding received from Northern
Innovation Program of the Northern Ontario Heritage Fund
Corporation
, that
Avalon is now in the process of preparing an updated technical
