Company Overview

Team: Click to ViewWebsite: avalonadvancedmaterials.comAvalon Advanced Materials Inc. is a Canadian mineral development company headquartered in Toronto and focused on specialty minerals with growing demand in new technology. Avalon has three wholly owned, advanced stage projects; the Separation Rapids Lithium Project near Kenora, Ontario, the East Kemptville Tin-Indium Project in SW Nova Scotia, and the Nechalacho Rare Earth Elements Project, NWT

Avalon’s current focus is Separation Rapids which hosts a large lithium pegmatite deposit that is well-suited for production of both lithium minerals for glass-ceramics and high purity lithium chemicals for batteries. The Company is moving forward with pilot plant work in 2017-18, to begin producing trial quantities of its lithium and other specialty minerals products. 
